    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1276184181" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15807445261422679987">Light reading about a rascal burro living in the Grand Canyon. Good books compel us to action...this book has sparked an interest in hiking the Grand Canyon. I have added this activity to my bucket list!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


