        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3399388812" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7450517254489015007">A very sweet book. I thought it was going to be too cute and childish, but it wasn’t. The illustrations were great, too — they showed Brighty’s personality very well. Interesting, too, that it was almost all factual! </span>

          </span>
