<div id="review_2772660088" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2772660088" />
    <a title="Julie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/91763420-julie"><img alt="Julie" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2772660088?book_show_action=true">Apr 05, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Julie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Julie" href="/user/show/91763420-julie">Julie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2772660088" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11629058171056200212">I loved this story especially Brighty! I have not had the pleasure of seeing The Grand Canyon but the writer, Marguerite Henry took me there with her descriptive writing..They didn’t think too highly of mountain lions in the early 1900’s. Curious to how they’re doing nowadays?<br/>Thanks for recommending it Briell- let’s go to The Grand Canyon soon!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


